extendedInfo.description: Foxy Photo Editor has everything you need to edit your pictures and create stunning compositions.Retouch your photos with a variety of tools and brushes. Transform, rotate, distort, clone. Add titles, balloons, shapes, clip arts. Make collages and compositions. Apply special effects and artistic filters. And much more..

reviews.title: Update app soon or DELETE
reviews.comment: I\'ve used your app about 3yrs. W/ Galaxy II, now I have a Galaxy III & now it force closes when I use paint (airbrush, paint brush w/the color pallet). Update to use w/Galaxy III or I will delete. 3 stars for you. FIVE ***** IF YOU FIX.
